CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 16, 2005

[Cite as 03/16/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1024.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2004-1588. State ex rel. Goudreau v. Kilbane-Koch.

Cuyahoga App. No. 84732. On motion to dismiss as moot. Motion to dismiss as moot sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
